# Discarded Submission Log

When MERGE determines a submission is a duplicate of an existing entry,
the submission's GE-ID is recorded here. The submitter can use this to
reconcile — knowing the canonical GE-ID lets them write a REVISE submission
targeting the correct existing entry instead.

---

| Discarded GE-ID | Conflicts with | Date | Reason |
|-----------------|----------------|------|--------|
